item.title: Is there anyway!
item.dc:creator: @Owner_Of_GdogScape Owner_Of_GdogScape
item.description:
@Owner_Of_GdogScape wrote:

Yes, go into your router and look in gaming & applications and see if your port (43594 or 5555) is in that list.
Unless your portforwarding with Utorrent (Not recommended) go into options and see if your “Port used for incoming connections” is set to 43593 or 5555.
